Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Software Development Engineer I position with GM Financial. I bring over three years of professional experience in fullstack web applications, cloud-native systems, and AI-powered solutions, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY with a 4.0 GPA.

