I have always been passionate about AI-powered transformation and digital innovation, and I am excited by GM Financial's commitment to using advanced machine learning and automation to reimagine customer interactions and modernize operations. I envision myself contributing my talent to furthering GM Financial's mission of achieving superior financial and operating results while adhering to the highest standards of business conduct. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

